content: I don't really identify with labels, but I think the SBNR concept is interesting. I've been feeling like I'm in a liminal space, where I'm not quite sure what I believe, but I'm open to exploring different possibilities. I guess you could say I'm more spiritual than religious, but I don't want to limit myself to any particular label or category. I just want to keep an open mind and heart, and see where my journey takes me.
